WEBVTT

p01
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.535
Look to the far right of the header.

p02
00:00:01.993 --> 00:00:05.552
Past Search, the location selector, and Ask Shyne, there is a small badge with your initials.

p03
00:00:05.851 --> 00:00:11.412
That is your account, and it rides along on every page.

p04
00:00:11.870 --> 00:00:13.597
Click it.

p05
00:00:13.597 --> 00:00:17.204
The menu opens with your name and your tenant code right at the top.

p06
00:00:17.204 --> 00:00:19.265
Get in the habit of reading that line.

p07
00:00:19.265 --> 00:00:22.872
It is the fastest way to confirm which company you are actually signed into.

p08
00:00:23.350 --> 00:00:24.177
Now the list.

p09
00:00:25.643 --> 00:00:28.580
Profile and Preferences hold your personal settings.

p10
00:00:29.781 --> 00:00:32.213
Notifications and Help Center do what they say.

p11
00:00:32.972 --> 00:00:36.831
The two you will reach for most are My Training and the Dark Mode switch.

p12
00:00:37.984 --> 00:00:42.522
One thing to leave alone for now: Logout, at the bottom, ends your session.

p13
00:00:43.080 --> 00:00:44.501
Flip the Dark Mode toggle.

p14
00:00:45.231 --> 00:00:48.366
The whole interface drops to a dark theme on the spot.

p15
00:00:48.625 --> 00:00:50.767
This is a display preference for you alone.

p16
00:00:51.002 --> 00:00:54.240
It changes nothing in the data and nothing for anyone else.

p17
00:00:54.790 --> 00:00:55.481
Toggle it back.

p18
00:00:55.910 --> 00:00:56.666
Light again.

p19
00:00:58.256 --> 00:01:03.410
Work in whichever theme is easier on your eyes; the switch is always safe to flip mid-shift.

p20
00:01:04.020 --> 00:01:06.597
Open the menu again and choose My Training.

p21
00:01:07.111 --> 00:01:11.406
That opens the WashCentral Academy, your learning home for this whole program.

p22
00:01:11.974 --> 00:01:16.189
Knowing it sits one click away in the account menu saves you hunting for it later.

p23
00:01:17.010 --> 00:01:18.342
Head back to the Command Center.

p24
00:01:18.773 --> 00:01:20.748
Same session, right where you left it.

p25
00:01:21.052 --> 00:01:28.221
From any screen, your initials in the corner are the door to your settings, your training, and, when you really mean it, the way out.

